{"tid":625170,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【女股神】405元以下撈騰訊 劉央：兩年升到1,000元！","createTime":"2018-04-11T08:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T08:27:26.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aabcbd77cb515cbabc8c0483e297e37587a8402c","tid":625170,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"牛三了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918fd8e18654f425c4e43b1a32c67dd91e5161c8","tid":625170,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"「中國女股神」西京投資主席劉央表示，看好5大板塊，包括醫療保健股、消費股、環境相關股、科技股及金融股，每個板塊佔投資比例均超過10%。<br />\n<br />\n她指，以市盈率等衝量港股值不值得買已不合事宜，「我以前是價值投資者（value investor），但2008年之後我是趨勢投資者。」她說，現在光說價值投資已沒有意義，「銀行股P/B 0.8，印度的銀行有4點幾，難道內銀比印度的差嗎？所以不要再跟我談value。」她說，價值投資的年代已結束，再談會被時代淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳雪蕾<br />\n<br />\n我的媽牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b79a2e18eb8e8e55f10a935d9eafee64870e4a","tid":625170,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"對於港股看法，「中國女股神」西京投資主席劉央表示，應該是觸底，近期兩次跌逾千點的股災已發生，但恒指仍在3萬點站得很穩，隨着更大的開放，港股的機會特別好。她續指，用了10年挑戰3萬點，35,000點將是年度目標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad7c2300872167aca382c109214aa9c74c09fe6","tid":625170,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"價值投資的年代已結束，再談會被時代淘汰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3880cbd5ff4db7c789ae97755270a542e261608d","tid":625170,"uid":171446,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16726173e6fdb5f9b22fab565e87ef8148a2f219","tid":625170,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:34:47.000Z","msg":"儘管被稱為「女股神」，但熱衷投資內地民企的劉央，其西京中國基金近年戰績不濟，繼2011年慘蝕三成後，去年亦僅錄得1.71%回報，連續兩年跑輸大市，其愛股銀基（886）更是越買越跌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f383307c720dba5f6c8385c0425cbc1bbdfd25fa","tid":625170,"uid":151107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:35:15.000Z","msg":"如果真係升得到1000蚊，我洗鬼等405蚊先買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940908c8302fb47eff396ff7aeddb430712af9cc","tid":625170,"uid":109386,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:45:41.000Z","msg":"我原本是一個投資者，現在我是一個賭徒，投資太撚on9，每年先得10%，現在我一天便100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cc4fa217906f36d353f6f65bc4989725a7303b","tid":625170,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"她說，現在光說價值投資已沒有意義，「銀行股P/B 0.8，印度的銀行有4點幾，難道內銀比印度的差嗎？所以不要再跟我談value。」<br />\n<br />\n岩牙岩牙"},{"pid":"670ef9a606eb66012275e05ff3452a3b50b77ce9","tid":625170,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"等睇佢當巴郡狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948506ab1990074c51e6ff4c6e77eb60ade4e55d","tid":625170,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"咋咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"